  "_comment": "This is a sample annotation scheme file. Load it via 'Import Scheme' in the app. Fields: name (string), version (string), description (string), levels (array of level objects), hasComment (boolean). Each level has: id (unique key used in annotation objects), label (display name), type ('select' or 'text'), required (boolean, default true). A 'select' level without 'dependsOn' needs an 'options' array [{value, label}]. A dependent 'select' level needs 'dependsOn' (parent level id) and 'optionsByParent' ({parentValue: [{value, label}]}).",
